<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٥٩٢ <span class="c2">(م)</span> - وَقَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1822">خَلِيفَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى بْنُ سَعِيدٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6361">مَنْصُورٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2238">سَالِمِ بْنِ أَبِي الْجَعْدِ </a>بِهَذَا. حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3902">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ مُحَمَّدٍ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">سُفْيَانُ </a>بِهَذَا وَقَالَ فِيهِ <span class="c2">«لَمَّا نَهَى النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَنِ الْأَوْعِيَةِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>